{
  "stem": "24814.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, I can remember a sense of hope that I heard among these people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were-- it's hard to believe, but they were talking about what's the best political system for Europe and the world.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, they were thinking even in the middle of this horror.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Social Democrats are not a good idea.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We need to do this, we need to do that, and they'd get into political arguments.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Liana, don't let Alex in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] This big Russian kid's coming.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Go ahead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Visitors at the door.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What-- what amazed me was that some of them said, well, we-- we figured we'd die, but we were sure some of us would live.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We sure you guys would get here some day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was a very moving thing to hear.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had even-- when they had bits of paper or something to write on, they were writing notes on things as remote as philosophy and government, and on and on and on.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what I went away with.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was an amazing sense of-- of courage that you saw in the survivors, when I finally left Dachau.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two weeks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By that time, the worst of it was over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Those who were going to die had died, and they were getting food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew I had to get back to my unit, because we were going to be moving around, doing assorted things.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got tapped, later on, the fighting was over, they broke up the combat units, and I was assigned to it-- because here I was major Medical Corps, fluent German, 7th Army headquarters in Heidelberg-- I got assigned to the-- an occupation job.",
      "word_count": 43
    }
  ],
